1989;;Scandal;;British;;Michael Caton-Jones;;John Hurt, Joanne Whalley, Bridget Fonda, Ian McKellen;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scandal_(1989_film);;An English bon-vivant osteopath is enchanted with a young exotic dancer and invites her to live with him. He serves as friend and mentor, and through his wide range of contacts and his parties she and her friend meet and date members of the Conservative Party. A scandal develops when her affair with the Minister of War comes to public attention.